    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class for all DCS-driven output objects on a <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref> board. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Subclass this to create custom output handlers. Objects declared at global scope self-register into the static linked list; <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup_1ab31c183f1fe58194e9c6e512fd9a0371" kindref="member">PanelGroup::loop()</ref> walks the list on every received CTRL_BCAST frame. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
